==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bow hand
<hw>Bow" hand`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Archery)</fld>
<def>The hand that holds the bow, <it>i. e.</it>, the left
hand.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Surely he shoots wide on the <qex>bow hand</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>The hand that draws the bow,
<it>i. e.</it>, the right hand.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bowhead</ent>⟦br⟧
